centralauth-account-exists: Nametavon hisobero ecod kard: nomi korbariji darxostşuda peş az in dar sistemi vurudi muştarak girifta şudaast.
centralauth-admin-already-unmerged: Çahiş az $1, allakaj az idƣom girifta şudaast
centralauth-admin-delete-description: Hazfi hisobi muştarak ba hamai tarçihoti muştarak xohad rason, çudo kardani hisobhoi mahallī, va ozod kardani nomi muştarak baroi giriftani digar korbar. Hamai hisobhoi mahallim vuçud xohand doşt. Guzarvoƶaho baroi hisobhoi mahallī peş az bargardonidan ba qimathoi peş xud peş az idƣom eçod şudand.
centralauth-admin-delete-success: Bomuvaffaqijat hisobi muştarak baroi "<nowiki>$1</nowiki>" hafz şud
centralauth-admin-no-unified: Heç hisobi jakkaşuda ba in nomi korbarī.
centralauth-admin-none-selected: Heç hisobi korbari baroi taƣjir intixob naşudaast.
centralauth-admin-permission: Tanho vikipedho metavonand hisobi korbariji digar korbaronro jakka kunand.
centralauth-admin-unmerge: Az idƣom ozod kardani mavodi intixobşuda
centralauth-admin-unmerge-success: Bo muvaffaqijat $1 {{PLURAL:$1|hisobro|hisobhoro}} az idƣom ozod kardam
centralauth-attach-list-attached: Hisobi korbariji muştarak "$1" şomili hisobhoi korbariji zerin meşavad:
centralauth-attach-success: Hisobi korbarī ba hisobi korbariji muştarak intiqol doda şud.
centralauth-attach-text: In hisobi korbarī hanūz ba hisobi korbariji muştarak intiqol doda naşudaast. Agar hisobi korbariji muştarak mutaaliq ba şumo ast, in hisobro ham metavoned bo vorid kardani kalimai uburi on ba hisobi korbariji muştarak jakka kuned:
centralauth-disabled-dryrun: Somonai jakka kardani hisobhoi korbarī dar holi hozir ba tavri ozmoişī va baroi raf'i erod fa'ol ast, binobar in jakka kardani hisobhoi voqeī hanuz fa'ol nest. Bubaxşed!
centralauth-editgroup-submit: Zaxirai taƣjiroti dodaşuda dar ixtijoroti gurūh
centralauth-editset-legend-new: Dar holi eçodi maçmū'ai vikiji nav
centralauth-editset-setexists: Maçmū'a bo on nom allakaj vuçud dorad
centralauth-error-locked: Şumo nametavoned viroiş kuned cun hisobi şumo basta ast.
centralauth-finish-incomplete:
Jakcand hisobho bo istifodai in guzarvoƶa idgom şudaand.
Digar hisobho to hol ta'jid naşudaand.
centralauth-finish-noconfirms: Heç hisobe bo istifodai in guzarvoƶa nametavonad ta'jid şavad.
centralauth-finish-send-confirmation: Kalimai ubur ba poctai elektronī firistoda şavad
centralauth-finish-text: Agar şumo sohibi in hisobho hasted, metavoned ravandi jakka kardani hisobhoi korbariro bo vorid kardani kalimai uburi sarosarī dar inço ba pojon birasoned:
centralauth-list-attached: Hisobi korbariji "$1" dar har jak az loihahoi zerin ba tavri xudkor ba hisobi korbariji muştarak pajvasta  ast:
centralauth-list-attached-dryrun: Hisobi korbariji "$1" dar har jak az loihahoi zerin ba tavri xudkor ba hisobi korbariji muştarak şumo pajvasta xohad şud:
centralauth-list-home-dryrun: Kalimai ubur va nişonai poctai elektroniji intixob şuda dar in viki baroi hisobi korbariji muştaraki şumo mavridi istifoda qaror xohad girift.
centralauth-list-unattached: Hisobi korbariji "$1"ro dar somonahoi zerin nametavon ba tavri xudkor mutaaliq ba şumo donist; bo ehtimoli zijod onho kalimai uburi digar az hisobi korbariji asliji şumo dorand:
centralauth-listusers-nolocal: zamima naşuda jo ba tavri mahallī vuçud nadorad
centralauth-merge-attempt: '''Mutobiqat dodani kalimai uburi vorid şuda bo hisobhoi idƣom naşudai boqimonda...'''
centralauth-merge-denied: Bubaxşed, şumo içozati dastrasī ba in sahifaro nadored.
centralauth-merge-dryrun-complete:
Tamomi hisobhoi vuçuddoşat metavonand ba tavri xudkor jakka karda şavand!

Jagon taƣjirote to hol ba hisobhoi şumo amalī naşudaand.
centralauth-merge-dryrun-home:
Sistemai kūconidan natavonist tasdiq kuned, ki şumo sohibi hisobi vikiji aslī baroi nomi korbariaton hasted.

Digar viki hamcun hisobi aslī baroi hisobi şumo muşaxxas şudaast; pajvandi zerro dunbol kuned va ba kūconidani hisobi xud xotima dihed.
centralauth-merge-dryrun-incomplete:
Şumo baroi davom qaror dored, ammo ba'ze hisobho nametavonand ba tavri xudkor ta'jid şavand jo mustaqiman kūconida şavand.
Şumo dertar metavoned inhoro idƣom kuned.

Heç taƣjirote ba hisobhoi şumo ançom naşudaand.
centralauth-merge-notlogged: Lutfan [{{fullurl:{{#special:UserLogin}}|returnto={{#special:MergeAccount}}}} ba sistem vorid şaved] to az idƣomi hisobhoi korbariaton itminon hosil kuned.
centralauth-merge-step1-detail:
Lutfan guzarvoƶai hisobatonro vorid kuned.
Guzarvoƶa va nişonai poctai elektroniji sabtşudai bo hisobhoi korbarī vikihoi digare muqoisa meşavad, to az mutobiqati onho itminon hosil gardad.
To zamone, ki şumo ta'jid nakuned, ki hama ciz durust ast, taƣjir surat naxohad girift.
centralauth-merge-step2-detail: Barxe az hisobhoi korbariro nametavon ba tavri xudkor bo xisobi vikiji aslī mutobiqat dod. Agar in xisobhoi korbarī ba şumo mutaaluq hastand, şumo metavoned in mas'alaro bo vorid kardani kalimai uburi in hisobho ta'jid kuned.
centralauth-merge-step3-detail: Şumo omodaed hisobi muştaraki xudro dar vikihoi zerin eçod kuned:
centralauth-mergeaccount-desc: Baroi Vurudi Jakkai Korbar [[Special:MergeAccount|jakcand hisobhoro jakka mekunad]]
centralauth-not-owner-text:
Hisobi korbariji "$1" ba tavri xudkor ba sohibi hisobi korbarī dar $2 ixtisos doda şud.

Agar şumo sohibi in hisob hasted, şumo metavoned ravandi jakka kardan hisobhoi korbariro bo vorid kardani kalimai uburi sarosarī dar in ço pojon birasoned:
centralauth-prefs-count-attached: Hisobi korbariji şumo dar $1 {{PLURAL:$1|loiha|loihaho}} fa'ol ast.
centralauth-prefs-count-unattached: Hisobhoi korbariji ta'jidnaşuda bo nomi şumo dar $1 {{PLURAL:$1|loiha|loihaho}} boqī memonad.
centralauth-prefs-detail-unattached: Somonai in loiha mavridi ta'jid baroi istifoda az hisobi korbariji muştarak qaror nagiriftaast.
centralauth-prefs-not-managed: Hisobi korbariji muştarak mavridi istifoda nest
centralauth-renameuser-reserved: Korbari $2 baroi hisobi muştarak nigoh doşta şudaast.
centralauth-rightslog-set-optout: bar asos az uzvijat dar omadan
centralauth-token-mismatch: Bubaxşed, mo natavonistem irsoli formi şumoro az sababi az bajn raftani dodahoi nişast ba ançom rasonem.
